body: "## Agent need\nAgents integrate with pm over MCP; that surface must expose the same primitives as the CLI and never drift, or agent integrations silently break.\n\n## Delivered surface (pm-5k4v)\nsrc/mcp/server + tool-definitions (28 tools); cli-contracts (flag/enum/tool-schema/parameter tables); pm contracts --full; compact MCP defaults; shared scope enum.\n\n## Verified by\nContract gates and tool-count assertions (4 places). Enduring agent-value statement for the MCP/contract capability; new work lands in pm-5k4v."
